Merge pull request #20 from andrewgaul/blobstore-read-npe

Address NPE when reading blob
JCLOUDS-1191: Avoid NPE and let commands properly print the stacktraces

Address NPE when reading blob

Object Boolean default value is null which causes a NPE when
auto-unboxing.  Primitive boolean default value is the expected false.
Avoid NPE when no location specified
Avoid NPE in blobstore read without an argument
Fixed a possible NPE when node creation fails.
Fixed a potential NPE in the managed shell table factory.

Fixed an NPE when invoking the blobsotre commands outside OSGi.
Fixed an NPE with the blobstore context factory.
Fixed NPE when listing images with some providers. Improved formatting of commands.
